  <rte>
    <name>Dow Crag and the Old Man of Coniston</name>
	<desc>This is a Lake District walk of some quality combing one of Lakeland's finest summits with one of its most popular. The walk description starts in Coniston village where there is ample parking except at busy times.</desc>
